Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.26,0:28:48.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果我不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.51,0:28:53.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你還能夠說是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.47,0:28:58.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}崩壞的砂器散落一地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.86,0:29:04.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}破碎的心能否重新拾起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.10,0:29:13.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何人的呼喚 幻化為耳鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.24,0:29:18.19,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時間似乎靜止
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:21.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}啊 覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.24,0:29:26.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}衝破這無邊的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.42,0:29:31.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}疾風一般逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.65,0:29:36.27,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}曾如行屍走肉一般
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.27,0:29:43.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我們 到城牆之外 再相見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:47.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在地圖之外
